---
// Sección Transformaciones con testimonios reales rediseñada
---

<section id="transformaciones" class="transformations-section">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
        </svg>
        Transformaciones Reales
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Historias que <span class="highlight">Inspiran</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Descubre cómo personas reales cambiaron su vida con JeanFit. ¡Tú puedes ser el próximo testimonio de éxito!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <!-- Testimonio 1 - Javiera -->
      <div class="testimonial-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="testimonial-image">
          <img src="/IMG_6046.jpeg" alt="Transformación de Javiera" />
          <div class="image-overlay">
            <div class="transformation-badge">
              <span>-10kg</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path
                d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p>
              "Bajé 10 kilos de grasa en un año. Lo mejor fue tener una planificación clara y motivación constante."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-info">
              <h4>Javiera</h4>
              <span>25 años</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating">
              <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 - Mariana -->
      <div class="testimonial-card featured" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="testimonial-image">
          <img src="/IMG_6359.jpeg" alt="Transformación de Mariana" />
          <div class="image-overlay">
            <div class="transformation-badge">
              <span>Tonificación</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path
                d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p>
              "Mejoré glúteos, cintura y tonifiqué brazos. El plan me ayudó a enfocarme y sentirme más segura
              entrenando."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-info">
              <h4>Mariana</h4>
              <span>28 años</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating">
              <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 3 - Miguel -->
      <div class="testimonial-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="testimonial-image">
          <img src="/IMG_6360.jpeg" alt="Transformación de Miguel" />
          <div class="image-overlay">
            <div class="transformation-badge">
              <span>+1 Año</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path
                d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p>
              "Entreno con JeanFIT y su plan con nutrición hace más de un año. He visto cambios sorprendentes tanto en
              mi físico como en mi energía diaria."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-info">
              <h4>Miguel</h4>
              <span>33 años</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating">
              <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Bottom -->
    <div class="cta-bottom" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
      <h3>¿Listo para tu propia transformación?</h3>
      <p>Únete a cientos de personas que ya cambiaron su vida con JeanFit</p>
      <a href="#servicios" class="cta-transformations-btn">
        <span>Comienza tu transformación</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .transformations-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 25%, #e2e8f0 50%, #f1f5f9 75%, #f8fafc 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .transformations-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container-custom {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* Section Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.1) 0%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-title .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd600 0%, #ed1c24 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Testimonials Grid */
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    contain: layout style paint;
  }

  .testimonial-card.featured {
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1.03);
    border-color: rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -6px, 0);
  }

  .testimonial-image {
    position: relative;
    height: 350px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonial-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0.5rem;
  }

  .transformation-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd600 0%, #ed1c24 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .testimonial-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-icon {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonial-quote p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #2d3748;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .author-info h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .author-info span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #718096;
  }

  .stars {
    color: #ffd600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* CTA Bottom */
  .cta-bottom {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .cta-bottom h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-bottom p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-transformations-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #dc2626 100%);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow:
      0 8px 20px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3),
      0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .cta-transformations-btn:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #ef4444 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .testimonial-card.featured {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .transformations-section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .container-custom {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .testimonial-image {
      height: 380px;
    }

    .testimonial-image img {
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .cta-bottom {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-bottom h3 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .testimonial-image {
      height: 380px;
    }

    .testimonial-image img {
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .testimonial-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
